## Text files 
# Normalize line endings to LF across platforms.
* text=auto eol=lf

# C/C++ sources and headers.
*.c      text eol=lf
*.cc     text eol=lf
*.cpp    text eol=lf
*.cxx    text eol=lf
*.h      text eol=lf
*.hh     text eol=lf
*.hpp    text eol=lf
*.inl    text eol=lf

# Build scripts & configs.
*.cmake       text eol=lf
CMakeLists.txt text eol=lf
*.sh          text eol=lf
*.command     text eol=lf
*.props       text eol=lf
*.yml         text eol=lf
*.yaml        text eol=lf
*.md          text eol=lf
*.txt         text eol=lf

## Binary/prebuilt artefacts
*.a         binary
*.lib       binary
*.dll       binary
*.dylib     binary
*.so        binary
*.metallib  binary
*.framework/** binary
*.dSYM/**   binary
*.dmg       binary

## Art assets
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.bmp  binary
*.psd  binary
*.ico  binary
*.ttf  binary
*.otf  binary
*.wav  binary
*.mp3  binary
*.ogg  binary

## GitHub linguist tweaks
# Hide vendored/compiled libraries from GitHub language stats.
lib/** linguist-vendored
